quote><br />\nx2<br />\n如果係有個咁gei老母, 有幾多錢都哂9氣"},{"pid":"547e5c7a2065a3f210a238fb31bab002764d1253","tid":219003,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你唔係當時人 你會知發生咩事？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有得幫 政府都唔理本土利益</blockquote><br />\n本身香港競爭大  <br />\n大個又冇咩路可以揀<br />\n果班唔洗政府幫ge中產先最迫得自己個小朋友緊</blockquote><br />\n倒轉左因果, 係政府唔幫呢班人次餘仲迫害佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29f883b250d7f2de11066f81678baff4635a943","tid":219003,"uid":105658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔係得個錢字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3218192a197a3f6b07771a4f4c73fc928c6eda0d","tid":219003,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"住過錦繡 非常唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e207b266f8088bd691bacafc2fd4223a0934962","tid":219003,"uid":81818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nrip"},{"pid":"107536c3f250f30e30775b3eb002ccda32a6d93c","tid":219003,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，呢排日日有"},{"pid":"8c3f8ebb27c8cef6fa4666c26c1041111676715d","tid":219003,"uid":11662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207512ec52d9f9bb64f2d2d91c4ea2d035361efd","tid":219003,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:57:20.0