ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d358bfa6b21cd2fcee51de65a28fa59d2f89481","tid":219003,"uid":74277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">積下厚德啦</span>"},{"pid":"8b6f4825beda43c8f86956672054f0b1985875f1","tid":219003,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住錦綉都唔一定好有錢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十幾年前到住過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過而家細路自殺都係學業壓力居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前交通唔方便個時 唔坐接駁巴士係錦綉出九龍要成個鐘 所以以前錦綉先賣得咁平"},{"pid":"dbe683b6a4aa5253483c5b50d4fdcce690cc970c","tid":219003,"uid":59777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>住錦綉都唔一定好有錢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十幾年前到住過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過而家細路自殺都係學業壓力居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前交通唔方便個時 唔坐接駁巴士係錦綉出九龍要成個鐘 所以以前錦綉先賣得咁平</blockquote><br />\n接駁巴出上水轉火車<br />\n<br />\n嗰時上水站好靜，邊似而家咁樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4012f7fb79ddc726a360f5eb0d4adec8cd90b6a","tid":219003,"uid":57837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:51:35.000Z","msg":"隔黎街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d38537b5c7c7cc3b11df01fd8c4ad360