gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836ec1a0f28500e90ab6458857d93d57461e9dc1","tid":219003,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/27/175404_0bd307a47f4ed00a074eebfffef25877.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F27%2F175404_0bd307a47f4ed00a074eebfffef25877.jpg&h=2a782b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺隔離見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港=無間道<br />\n支那人,港支人,廢港,垃圾港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a0252d86f547df7cebe50cbfc163471a3ed001","tid":219003,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解自殺一定關錢事<br />\n唔係話積唔積口德 係你一開口謝顯示你係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普遍人都唔會太明唔需要追求基本物質滿足之後嘅心理境界，不過有乜嘢會令一個小康之家後代自殺，黎黎去去都係家族壓迫或者出面奶咗嘢面對唔到/不知所措</blockquote><br />\n根本唔係普唔普遍既問題<br />\n有同理心大概都會明人諗咩<br />\n只可以話班連登仔有反社會傾向</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係反映左而家個社會連基本物質滿足都已經冇幾多人做到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n這就是垃圾港,衰過USA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322bbb970ab7c7ea7903809db071e20579a3d616","tid":219003,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:07:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"672aa22b11be299cccb4fd3bcfad3b9865f51b7d","tid":219003,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你唔係當時人 你會知發生咩事？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有得幫 政府都唔理本土利益</blockquote